<h2>4 - Lake Murray Dam to Broad/Congaree confluence (Saluda Shoals County Park to Senate Street Boat ramp off US #1)</h2>
<table class='data_table river-stats'>
<tr class='row-1'>
<th>Usual Difficulty</th>
<td>II-IV (for normal flows) </td>
</tr>
<tr class='row-2'>
<th>Length</th>
<td>11 Miles </td>
</tr>
</table>
<div class='river-photo'>
<div class='controls'>
